OL,3,CAir hostess admits trying to board
OL,4,CHeathrow flight over aircrew alcohol
OL,5,Climit
OL,7,FAn air hostess has admitted trying to
OL,8,Fboard a flight at Heathrow Airport
OL,9,Fwhilst drunk at more than 12 times the
OL,10,Faircrew alcohol limit.
OL,12,FJessica Kostakopoulou, 43, stated she
OL,13,Fhad not been drinking when she was
OL,14,Fstopped by security in Terminal 2 of
OL,15,Fthe airport on March 22.
OL,17,FPolice were then called.
