OL,5,Climit
OL,7,FThe defendant, who had been working
OL,8,Ffor Scandinavian Air since October
OL,9,Flast year, "appeared unsteady on her
OL,10,Ffeet and slurred her words" and
OL,11,Fsmelled of alcohol during the
OL,12,Fincident, prosecutor Reem Khatib told
OL,13,FUxbridge Magistrates' Court.
OL,15,FSubsequent breathalyser tests showed
OL,16,Fshe had 254 milligrams of alcohol per
OL,17,F100 millilitres of blood in her system.
OL,19,FThe legal limit is 20 milligrams for
OL,20,Faircrew, the court heard.
