OL,7,FThe alcohol limit for drivers is 80
OL,8,Fmilligrams per 100 millilitres of
OL,9,Fblood in England, Wales and Northern
OL,10,FIreland.
OL,12,FKostakopoulou, of Claremont Road,
OL,13,FWindsor, pleaded guilty to carrying
OL,14,Fout an activity, namely going through
OL,15,Fsecurity, which was ancillary to an
OL,16,Faviation function at the court on
OL,17,FTuesday 9 September.
