OL,7,FAmber Pierce, defending, told the
OL,8,Fcourt the defendant was not a
OL,9,Fsupervisor on the flight she intended
OL,10,Fto board and "no direct harm" was
OL,11,Fcaused as a result of her actions.
OL,13,FThe court heard Kostakopoulou, who was
OL,14,Fof previous good character and had
OL,15,Fbeen working in the aviation industry
OL,16,Ffor more than 20 years, resigned from
OL,17,Fher role as an air steward immediately
OL,18,Fafter the incident occurred.
