OL,7,FThe defendant was fined #623,
OL,8,Fincluding a victim surcharge and legal
OL,9,Fcosts, to be paid in monthly
OL,10,Finstalments.
OL,12,FKostakopoulou said: "I feel very
OL,13,Fashamed and embarrassed about
OL,14,Feverything that happened.
OL,16,F"I'm trying to amend my ways now and
OL,17,Fstart a new job. I'm very sorry."
